Detailed Description

cvmx_pci_pkt_credits#

PCI_PKT_CREDITS0 = PCI Packet Credits For Output 0

Used to decrease the number of packets to be processed by the host from Output-0 and return buffer/info pointer pairs to OCTEON Output-0. The value in this register is acted upon when the least-significant-byte of this register is written.
